{"tid":503500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"昨錄9.8℃　8人低溫症入院","createTime":"2017-12-19T02:17:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T09:07:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"769539484cd141d1b2df7ad869e900175ab1990f","tid":503500,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T02:17:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171219/20248968\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171219%2F20248968&d=yxQoWzmCNdQRN7MG33MBy0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=0b387556\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171219%2F20248968&h=7c46f2af\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171219/20248968</a><br />\n<br />\n昨錄9.8℃　8人低溫症入院<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171219/large/1218davies1007.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171219%2Flarge%2F1218davies1007.jpg&h=d7897a71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n昨日錄得入冬以來最低氣溫9.8℃，學生上學時需加穿厚衣。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】寒冷天氣持續，天文台昨日錄得入冬以來最低氣溫，僅9.8℃。公立醫院由周日下午5時至昨下午5時，共收到8人因體溫過低，需送往急症室接受治療，當中5人情況嚴重。醫管局發言人表示，因低溫症狀而入院的8名病人，年齡介乎20歲至95歲，只有1人已經出院，其餘7人截至昨日仍留醫。<br />\n<br />\n今11℃至16℃<br />\n<br />\n醫管局發言人指，低溫症泛指體溫跌至35℃以下，會影響器官機能；若跌至28℃至30℃，則屬危險期，患者更隨時有生命危險。衞生防護中心發言人亦提醒市民，寒冷天氣容易引起或加劇疾病，長者、心臟或呼吸系統疾病患者和其他長期病患者應特別小心。<br />\n<br />\n由於強烈冬季季候風繼續支配廣東，天文台預料今日仍然寒冷，市區氣溫介乎11℃至16℃，新界北部最低更只有7℃至9℃。展望明日氣溫料介乎11℃至17℃，隨後數天氣溫逐步上升，周日「平安夜」最高20℃。<br />\n<br />\n民政事務總署昨日在各區開放共17間臨時避寒中心，供有需要的市民避寒。今日日間寒冷天氣警告仍然生效期間會繼續開放。<br />\n<br />\n■記者于健民<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171219/large/a0803a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171219%2Flarge%2Fa0803a.gif&h=b9b3ef6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d76963708f7f2c3196c4c026497eff8f94887ee","tid":503500,"uid":13802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T02:19:04.000Z","msg":"姐係有個20歲?"},{"pid":"7682db8bcff5ed924aa405566c8900873271e888","tid":503500,"uid":33868,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T02:19:37.000Z","msg":"廢物"},{"pid":"619c58ac8f8991908133435aed9431606b87100d","tid":503500,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T02:19:53.000Z","msg":"呢個溫度唔錯, 凍, 但唔會太低"},{"pid":"48eddb7dfdd7e58359b71a2917d79669c4f94c47","tid":503500,"uid":90863,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T02:20:39.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"cfcdf99e1730ea665c30a9200fb593827e8c1379","tid":503500,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T02:21:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>姐係有個20歲?</blockquote><br />\n不能自理？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76651a82b4416dde6579b5a3d2c98c8045c0336e","tid":503500,"uid":60655,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T02:21:57.000Z","msg":"邊個巴打咁虧，自已出黎認左佢"},{"pid":"5f304fec8962654beee847974d8f6695734609cd","tid":503500,"uid":42200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T02:24:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">濕</span>"},{"pid":"cf84f4b7413873f046ca50748b65ab387f24cbd7","tid":503500,"uid":116289,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T02:25:02.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"fed9de855994704f0f57e2a1dff5c0d030932e82","tid":503500,"uid":144529,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T02:59:23.000Z","msg":"會唔會太廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b2b5279c23929cc77f6cee5fdd9f61ef59149b","tid":503500,"uid":31927,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T03:11:19.000Z","msg